For the development of condensed the software QA to all tasks after the completion of the testing method. Their problem is that it brings to the team huge costs and put the whole project in high risk. In the testing phase, developers do their best to ensure that their code with few defects. Then the tester try to reveal every possible defects in software.
The hasty developments may save a moment of time for the team. If there are some major development problems without considering the right from the start, it will be lead to spend more time eventually. The result is a waste of a lot of team resources to repair and to design code. Software quality assurance has important role in the entire software development process. 
